  "synopsis": "Newly-awakened hunter Habin Hyun is mankind’s only hope, but after many years of the minimum wage grind, all she wants to do is take a break. Unfortunately for her, her ridiculously broken stats catapult her into the spotlight in more ways than one. With every guild scouting her, the System’s bounty on her head, and love interests appearing from every angle, it seems Habin’s going to have to take her new friends and unlikely allies all the way to the Tower’s top, whether she likes it or not.\n\n(Source: Tapas)",
